title: Daily Review with Clay and Buck - Jul 29 2022
itunes:title: Daily Review with Clay and Buck - Jul 29 2022
description:
President Trump joins Clay & Buck live from Trump National Golf Club in Bedminster, NJ. Crime in America is one of the major issues facing American voters. Nancy Pelosi is going to China and China has threatened her plane arriving there- what should the US do?

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
